dart_amqp_client.description: Dart package that simplifies the handling of AMQP (Advanced Message Queuing Protocol) connections, channels, and associated callbacks. It provides an easy-to-use interface for establishing and managing connections to AMQP servers, enabling you to focus on your application's logic without dealing with low-level AMQP details.

Dart package that simplifies the handling of AMQP (Advanced Message Queuing Protocol) connections, channels, and associated callbacks. It provides an easy-to-use interface for establishing and managing connections to AMQP servers, enabling you to focus on your application's logic without dealing with low-level AMQP details.
